export XDG_SESSION_ID="${XDG_SESSION_ID:-323544}"
export SHLVL="${SHLVL:-1}"
export SSH_TTY="${SSH_TTY:-/dev/pts/19}"
export SSH_CLIENT="${SSH_CLIENT:-172.24.5.99 42142 22}"
export HISTFILESIZE="${HISTFILESIZE:-10000}"
export HISTCONTROL="${HISTCONTROL:-ignoredups:erasedups}"
export PWD="${PWD:-/home/madsbk/benchpress}"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="${LD_LIBRARY_PATH:-/home/madsbk/.local/lib:}"
export LOGNAME="${LOGNAME:-madsbk}"
export USER="${USER:-madsbk}"
export MAIL="${MAIL:-/var/mail/madsbk}"
export HOME="${HOME:-/home/madsbk}"
export SSH_CONNECTION="${SSH_CONNECTION:-172.24.5.99 42142 130.225.212.177 22}"
export HISTSIZE="${HISTSIZE:-10000}"
export DISPLAY="${DISPLAY:-:0}"
export _="${_:-./bohrium-by-night/run_benchmark.py}"
export PATH="${PATH:-/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/usr/games:/usr/local/games}"
export BH_CONFIG=/tmp/bh-job-541c1ba4-700d-488f-89ce-08d3852a86fe.sh_2.config.ini

#SBATCH -J 'LU Factorization'
#SBATCH -o /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.out
#SBATCH -e /tmp/bh-slurm-%%j.err
echo "[bridge]
type = bridge
children = node

[visualizer]
type = ve
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_visualizer.so

[proxy]
type = vem
port = 4200
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_proxy_server.so
children = node

[cluster]
type = vem
children = node
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_cluster.so

[node]
type = vem
children = gpu
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_vem_node.so

[cpu]
type = ve
compiler_cmd = "gcc -I/home/madsbk/.local/include -I/home/madsbk/.local/include/bohrium -I/home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include -lm -O3 -march=native -fopenmp -fPIC -std=c99 -x c -shared - -o "
object_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/objects
kernel_path = /home/madsbk/.local/var/bohrium/kernels
template_path = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/templates
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_cpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_matmul.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_visualizer.so,/home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_fftw.so

[gpu]
type = ve
include = /home/madsbk/.local/share/bohrium/include
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
libs = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
children = cpu

[transitive_reduction]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_transitive_reduction.so
children = cpu

[pprint]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_pprint.so
children = cpu

[validate]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_validate.so
children = cpu

[range]
type = filter
impl = /home/madsbk/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu

" > /tmp/bh-job-541c1ba4-700d-488f-89ce-08d3852a86fe.sh_2.config.ini
cd /home/madsbk/bohrium
 /usr/bin/time -v -o /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-541c1ba4-700d-488f-89ce-08d3852a86fe.sh-2.time python benchmark/Python/lu.py --size=100 --bohrium=True 1> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-541c1ba4-700d-488f-89ce-08d3852a86fe.sh-2.out 2> /home/madsbk/benchpress/bh-job-541c1ba4-700d-488f-89ce-08d3852a86fe.sh-2.err

rm /tmp/bh-job-541c1ba4-700d-488f-89ce-08d3852a86fe.sh_2.config.ini
